Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什麼動畫呀 請清清楚楚地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,回想起來吧
